quran[6{c,v,t}:
13,29,phir jin logon ne dawat haq ko maana aur naik amal kiye woh khush naseeb hain aur un ke liye acha injaam hai
13,30,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, aِsi shaan se hum ne tum ko rasool bana kar bheja hai, aik aisi qoum mein jis se pehlay bohat si qoumain guzar chuki hain, taakay tum inn logon ko woh pegham sunaaoo jo hum ne tum par nazil kya hai, iss haal mein ke yeh apne nihayat meharban khuda ke kafir banay hue hain inn se kaho ke wohi mera rab hai, uss ke siwa koi mabood nahi hai, usi par mein ne bharosa kya aur wohi mera Malja o mava hai"
13,31,"aur kya ho jata agar koi aisa quran utaar diya jata jis ke zor se pahar chalne lagtay, ya zameen shaqq ho jati, ya murdy qabron se nikal kar bolnay lagtay? ( is terhan ki nishanain dikha dena kuch mushkil nahi hai ) balkay sara ikhtiyar hi Allah ke haath mein hai phir kya ahal imaan ( abhi taq kufar ki talab ke jawab mein kisi nishani ke zahuur ki aas laga ye baithy hain aur woh yeh jaan kar ) mayoos nahi ho gay ke agar Allah chahta to saaray insanon ko hadaayat day deta? jin logon ne khuda ke sath kufar ka rawayya ikhtiyar kar ray kha hai unn par un ke krtoton ki wajah se koi nah koi aafat aati hi rehti hai, ya un ke ghar ke qareeb kahin nazil hoti hai yeh silsila chalta rahay ga yahan taq ke Allah ka wada aan poora ho yaqeenan Allah apne waday ki khilaaf warzi nahi karta"
13,32,"tum se pehlay bhi bohat se Rasolo-n ka mazaq uraya ja chuka hai, magar mein ne hamesha munkir yan ko dheel di aur aakhir-kaar un ko pakar liya, phir dekh lau ke meri saza kaisi sakht thi"
13,33,"phir kya woh jo aik aik mutnaqas ki kamaai par nazar rakhta hai ( uss ke muqablay mein yehjasartain ki ja rahi hain ke ) logon ne uss ke kuch shareektehra rakhay hain? ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho ( agar waqai woh khuda ke apne banaye hue shareek hain to ) zara unn ke na meem lau ke woh kon hain? kya tum Allah ko aik nai baat ki khabar day rahay ho jisay woh apni zameen mein nahi jaanta? ya tum log bas yuhin jo mun mein aata hai keh daaltay ho? haqeeqat yeh hai ke jin logon ne dawat haq ko maan-ne se inkaar kya hai un ke liye unn ki makaryan khushnuma bana di gayi hain aur woh raah raast se rok diye gay hain, phir jis ko Allah gumraahi mein pheink day ussay koi raah dikhaane wala nahi hai"
13,34,"aisay logon ke liye duniya ki zindagi hi mein azaab hai, aur akhirat ka azaab uss se bhi ziyada sakht hai koi aisa nahi jo unhen khuda se bachanay wala ho"
